	<div class="group">
		<img src="http://foodsense.is/uploads/post-images/MushroomGemelli_blog.jpg" class="post-image border" alt="image" />			<p><em>Over the holiday break, my brother was craving wild mushroom soup. So, I did a Google search and eventually came up with this <a href="http://www.seasaltwithfood.com/2011/06/mushroom-soup.html">recipe</a> - which turned out fantastically. So, I was incredibly excited to see that Ruth from v:gourmet also recently created a mushroom dish perfectly suited for winter.</em></p>
