	<header>
	<h1><a href="http://foodsense.is/blog/to-eating-better-in-2012">To Eating Better in 2012</a></h1>
		</header>
		
	<div class="group">
		<img src="http://foodsense.is/uploads/post-images/Eating_Better_2012.jpg" class="post-image border" alt="image" />			<p>On New Year&#8217;s Day, as I had breakfast with my family, we went around the table and talked about what we want to accomplish in 2012, what we want to do better. Knock on wood, we are all in good health, but still, almost everyone had a goal related to their health - cook at home more frequently, train for a half-marathon, eat smaller portions, brush every night before bed, lose 10 pounds.</p>
		<p><a href="http://foodsense.is/blog/to-eating-better-in-2012">Continue reading &raquo;</a></p>	</div>
		
