		</header>
		
	<div class="group">
		<img src="http://foodsense.is/uploads/post-images/CauliflowerSoup_blog.jpg" class="post-image border" alt="image" />			<p>I, too, couldn&#8217;t believe it when I didn&#8217;t see potato, soy milk, or some other kind of &#8220;creamy&#8221; ingredient in this soup. It calls for six ingredients, primarily cauliflower, and a lot of water. Won&#8217;t this taste too much like, well&#8230;watery cauliflower?</p>
		<p><a href="http://foodsense.is/blog/cauliflower-soup">Continue reading &raquo;</a></p>	</div>
		
